36
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:29,600
Xiao Tuo, I've always wanted to ask you something.

37
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:36,300
Did you sign up for a medical university as one of the options?

38
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:42,300
Yes, I did.

39
00:03:43,100 --> 00:03:47,900
But I scored too low, so I lied and said I never applied.

40
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:55,500
But I would have gone to a medical university if I had...

41
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:00,300
scored high enough.

42
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:11,300
Y-You know what? Back then,

43
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:18,000
I went through so much to enter the medical university.

44
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:25,800
I had to bike for two hours to the cram school after class every day.

45
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:28,900
It was so cold in the winter I couldn't take it.

46
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:33,000
In the end, I set up a bed in the storage room

47
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:38,000
in my classmate's house in the county and slept there.

48
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,500
The winter nights were freezing.

49
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:45,900
I dared not take off my shoes or my hat.

50
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:49,300
It was so tough.

51
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:54,600
But I devoted myself to the medical university despite all that.

52
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:58,500
Because it had always been my dream.

53
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:01,600
My ambition.

54
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:06,600
Soon after I got enrolled, I met your mom.

55
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:11,400
We didn't meet at school. She was at the nursing school.

56
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:17,700
The medical university changed my life.

57
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:21,500
It offered me love, marriage,

58
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:25,500
a job, a family,

59
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:29,200
and two sons.

60
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:36,800
You've never mentioned it.

61
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:40,200
You've been way too busy.

62
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:48,400
It's not because of that,

63
00:05:50,900 --> 00:05:53,000
but my negligence.

64
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,000
Over the years,

65
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:05,300
