All ready?

183
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:13,600
- Yeah. 
 - Yeah.

184
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,800
- All right. 
 - Where are you going?

185
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:20,000
- Come on. 
 - Just stay. We're here for the senior.

186
